oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Lester Flatt and the Nashville Grass with the Osborne Brothers at Early Times Ranch (18129)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Flatt, Lester; Nashville Grass (Musical group); Osborne Brothers; Martha White Foods; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on brown) announcing Lester Flatt and the Nashville Grass with the Osborne Brothers at Early Times Ranch on October 15 and 16. Poster features metal photoplates of Lester Flatt and the Nashville Grass, the Osborne Brothers, and of the sponsor, Martha White Flour Co. To see the business record associated with this poster, visit https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/49053/
